title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4822.16 - Lessor may only make premises available to licensed organization
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4822.16 - Lessor may only make premises available to licensed organization

State Regulations

No lessor shall make such lessor's premises available for
the conduct of bingo to other than an authorized organization licensed to
conduct bingo. Notes
